text: Sunanda Patnaik (7 November 1934 - 19 January 2020) was an Indian classical singer of Gwalior gharana. She was thought to be one of the great singers of Hindustani music.NME: Grand Dames of Hindustani Music - Sunanda Patnaik ==References== Category:1934 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Indian singers
title: Sunanda Patnaik
